@startuml
title FEC eRegulations - Deployment and Data Flow Sequence Diagram

actor Developer
participant "tasks.py\n(Invoke Automation)" as Tasks
participant "Cloud Foundry\n(cloud.gov)" as CF
participant "Django Application\n(fec-eregs)" as Django
participant "regulations-parser" as Parser
participant "regulations-core\n(Data Service)" as Core
participant "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB
participant "ElasticSearch" as ES
participant "CMS\n(Content Management)" as CMS
participant "API Service" as API
actor "End User" as User

== Deployment Phase ==

Developer -> Tasks: invoke deploy
activate Tasks

Tasks -> Tasks: Git operations\n(GitPython)
Tasks -> CF: cf login
activate CF
Tasks -> CF: cf target -s <space>
Tasks -> CF: cf push -f manifest_*.yml
CF -> CF: Parse manifest_*.yml\n(resources, routes, services)
CF -> Django: Deploy application
activate Django
CF -> DB: Provision PostgreSQL service
activate DB
CF -> ES: Provision ElasticSearch service
activate ES
Tasks -> CF: Set network policies
Tasks --> Developer: Deployment complete
deactivate Tasks

== Data Loading Phase ==

Developer -> Parser: Execute load_regs scripts
activate Parser
Parser -> Parser: Parse FEC regulations\n(Custom preprocessors)
Parser -> Core: POST parsed regulation data
activate Core
Core -> DB: Store regulation hierarchy\n(MPTT structure: lft, rght, tree_id)
Core -> DB: Store version diffs\n(regcore_diff table)
DB --> Core: Data stored
Core --> Parser: Confirmation
deactivate Core
Parser -> ES: Index regulation content\n(keyword search)
ES --> Parser: Indexed
Parser --> Developer: Regulations loaded
deactivate Parser

== Runtime Data Flow ==

User -> Django: HTTP Request\n(Browse regulations)
activate Django

Django -> Django: Process request\n(WSGI entry point)
Django -> CMS: Fetch CMS content\n(FEC_CMS_URL)
activate CMS
CMS --> Django: Return content
deactivate CMS

Django -> Core: Request regulation data\n(REST API)
activate Core
Core -> DB: Query regulations\n(regcore_document MPTT)
activate DB
DB --> Core: Hierarchical data
deactivate DB
Core --> Django: Regulation structure
deactivate Core

Django -> Django: Render templates\n(Django templating)
Django -> Django: Apply SCSS styling\n(Compiled CSS)
Django --> User: HTML Response

== User Search Flow ==

User -> Django: Search request\n(keyword query)
Django -> API: Forward search query\n(API_KEY, API_VERSION)
activate API
API -> ES: Execute search\n(keyword matching)
ES --> API: Search results
deactivate ES
API --> Django: Formatted results
deactivate API
Django -> Core: Fetch detailed regulation data
activate Core
Core -> DB: Query specific regulations
DB --> Core: Regulation details
deactivate DB
Core --> Django: Complete data
deactivate Core
Django --> User: Search results page

== Version Diff Flow ==

User -> Django: Compare regulation versions
Django -> Core: Request version diff
activate Core
Core -> DB: Query regcore_diff table\n(serialized differences)
DB --> Core: Diff data
deactivate DB
Core --> Django: Version differences
Django -> Django: Render diff view\n(Template inheritance)
Django --> User: Comparison view

deactivate Django
deactivate CF

@enduml
